{"tid":1071150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1981年跳軌奇案的真相","createTime":"2019-03-21T06:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T12:57:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4154b348b63364a57ca498be2d492b3b292e30","tid":1071150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:52:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190321/20637599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F20637599&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3IVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=e84a5934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F20637599&h=82363845\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190321/20637599</a><br />\n<br />\n1981年跳軌奇案的真相 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190321/large/1553074690_d070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190321%2Flarge%2F1553074690_d070.jpg&h=7d685add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n昨天談及1981年11月油麻地地鐵站有少女跳軌，然後離奇消失，拙文刊登不出半日，事情發展便有重大突破。多年來大家把此事當作靈異故事，我卻深深懷疑，理由有二。第一，近年不少靈異節目聲稱收到「堅料」，有說少女靈魂出竅，有說她墳場撞鬼，但結局萬變不離其宗，都是「女主角死了」，問題是：如果消息可靠，為什麼總說不出主角的姓名背景？既然事主不在人世，還有什麼需要避忌？第二，跳軌還跳軌，死還死，兩件事不該混為一談。因此我昨天大膽推測：事主沒死，只是掉入月台下空隙位置，然後趁亂逃去。<br />\n<br />\n昨天早上我在FB分享拙文時，補了一句按語：「呢單嘢大家一直當鬼古，但我寫文前卜過一卦（《睽之无妄》），相信個女仔根本冇死。」兩小時後，兩位讀者先後聯絡我，證實了我的推測！揭曉真相前，先講清楚三件事：一，消息人士並非來歷不明的網友，兩人我都曾經聯繫，知悉其姓名背景，並確信他們沒有理由說謊；二，兩人皆認識跳軌主角本人；三，他們各自講述自己知道的故事，所言完全一致。<br />\n<br />\n好了，以下就是真相：1981年油麻地站的跳軌者，並非司機所形容的十七八歲少女，而是二十二歲女子，所以她今年已六十歲了。她當時沒穿校服，只是身穿白衣。為什麼要跳軌呢？事主當年生了第一胎後，患上躁鬱症，常聽到一把聲音在耳邊罵她，叫她去死，結果她真的跳下路軌。但墮軌後，她忽然聽到另一把聲音說：「唔好死。」於是在千鈞一髮之際，她伏在路軌中間，沒被輾過，待列車停定，她才悄悄爬回月台，驚惶失措地離開。後來她信了基督教，將那兩把聲音理解為魔鬼與耶穌，也曾對教友提及此事。多年前曾有知情者在網上澄清，但因為不及靈異故事有趣，真相反被埋沒。<br />\n<br />\n恕我不能公開事主姓名，因為她現在是位平凡婦人，過着安穩生活，決不希望被人打擾。我今天寫出來，純粹為了澄清事實──不扮陰森，只求傳真。真相大白後，是彩蛋時段。剛才不是說我事前占了一卦，卜事主墮軌狀況嗎？《睽之无妄》有兩爻變，爻辭分別是「遇主于巷，无咎」和「悔亡，厥宗噬膚，往何咎」。我斷易從來不按古義，反而根據「隨機應變」原則，所以後句我解作：事主墮軌後只受皮外傷（噬膚），沒大礙。前句則有點費解：「巷」我解為狹窄的通道，即月台下空隙，只想不通何謂「遇主」──但當我知道事主把墮軌後聽到的「唔好死」理解為主耶穌的聲音時，我便恍然大悟了。  <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾 <br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n孩童勿近神父 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n即使受傷也珍惜自己 (李碧華)"},{"pid":"8cc5829f3b802088292469b55c9e0b7776e97b47","tid":1071150,"uid":228431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:57:04.000Z","msg":"GANTZ"},{"pid":"94d4416ba79091b399d9126f5ba5176208ea358d","tid":1071150,"uid":228532,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:58:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10e9e51a0ca196a397c33da215bbb2650acfdae5","tid":1071150,"uid":128223,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c17aa40fc10e10843ff774e8f8de2e9035affb8","tid":1071150,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"咁大件事爬上月台冇人知"},{"pid":"ff444a777a719790925b2f1febe6259f2da454b2","tid":1071150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"地鐵史上最神秘的意外<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1070193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1070193</a>"},{"pid":"f673082a8eb232686c9599b255f226f666482cb2","tid":1071150,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c17aa40fc10e10843ff774e8f8de2e9035affb8","tid":1071150,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"咁大件事爬上月台冇人知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點可能會無人知，仲要之前咁多人話見到補人跳落去"},{"pid":"c05d18d90c5fed17281402f1b3a70cee01ada0d9","tid":1071150,"uid":10757,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"因此我昨天大膽推測：事主沒死，只是掉入月台下空隙位置，然後趁亂逃去。<br />\n屌你老母有冇職業道德架 咁樣呃稿費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adfbecdbf2cd2566998c9de1ad3eb04429fd775","tid":1071150,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"354a65748d9017ac0f3acacac53094ad529d7a40","tid":1071150,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:12:36.000Z","msg":"乜都唔公開，我話係觀音顯靈救咗佢都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8062d657f41757f80791e07c9221ac09605314d2","tid":1071150,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"Propro有講 去youtube睇仲好"},{"pid":"64937ad721d861f15521a92e63147dd47627c818","tid":1071150,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"事實上呢個講法可信過撞鬼"},{"pid":"f7fb7ec40c9d56a0a3df83c9a4e830e0026b3857","tid":1071150,"uid":100045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"係啦係啦叻啦叻啦知你好撚型"},{"pid":"af8956db690d750fe9ca4856d1b81363f9f272be","tid":1071150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff444a777a719790925b2f1febe6259f2da454b2","tid":1071150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"地鐵史上最神秘的意外<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1070193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1070193</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190320/20636808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20636808&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3IVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=89e3f4c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20636808&h=f0e5fcbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190320/20636808</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地鐵史上最神秘的意外 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190320/large/1552986029_2b85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190320%2Flarge%2F1552986029_2b85.jpg&h=7f2f5286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n前天地鐵炒車，事屬罕見，但並非無法解釋。若要數地鐵史上最神秘，甚或最令人毛骨悚然的意外，我會說是一九八一年油麻地站女學生墮軌奇案。這件事千真萬確，電視報紙皆有報導，市民茶餘飯後議論紛紛，很多讀者想必記得。<br />\n<br />\n八一年十一月十日下午一點半，一列從中環往觀塘的地鐵進入油麻地站，司機突見一名身穿白色校服的女學生躍下月台，馬上煞車。惜為時已晚，司機感到列車已輾過女生。據說月台上亦有目擊者，高叫「有人跌落路軌」。警員、消防員接報到場，用器械吊起車廂，爬入車底檢查，沿着路軌搜索，最後一無所獲，甚至連血也不見一滴。下午二時四十分，營救人員無功而退，地鐵恢復通車。翌日報章有標題寫道：「疑有一女學生墮軌被捲入車底 地鐵佐敦至旺角三站 昨暫停通車逾一小時 千餘乘客受影響 檢查無發現」。墮軌後失蹤固然離奇，但地鐵三站下午暫停服務，也只影響區區「千餘乘客」，今天看來也有點超現實。<br />\n<br />\n地鐵發言人稱，司機健康良好，沒精神病，休假兩天後照常上班。那麼司機和月台的市民是否撞鬼呢？我小時候已聽聞以下「真相」，據說來自少女的同學：跳軌少女，其實是同場另一少女的魂魄，兩者一模一樣，少女看見「自己」跳軌，驚惶失措回家，兩日後病死。多年來，靈異節目主持人不斷試圖解謎（網上還流傳一段偽造的「現場短片」），都未能令我信服。警方推測，跳軌少女可能躲在月台下的空隙，沒被列車輾過，事後趁亂逃去；也有心理學者說目擊者有「集體幻覺」。<br />\n<br />\n這都市傳說流傳了三十七年，不得其解，今天重溫此事，並非旨在測試你的年齡記性，我只想提出一個大家都忽略了的角度&mdash;&mdash;那少女可能尚在人間。憑常理，警方的推測最有可能。跳軌少女假如活着，今天不過五十四歲。我們能否通過互聯網找到當日的目擊者，把口供綜合起來重組案情呢？甚至異想天開一點，我們可以聯絡到跳軌主角嗎？希望會有答案。  <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾 <br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n吃了屎不許說臭 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n莊閒不分 (高慧然)"},{"pid":"051616252980d4365cc9d59281ccde81def52059","tid":1071150,"uid":143122,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"燥鬱症係情緒病唔會有幻聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幻聽就係思覺失調<br />\n真係9up當秘笈"},{"pid":"398e81822f91b2ccd911bd7cada62dc707de3bfa","tid":1071150,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8062d657f41757f80791e07c9221ac09605314d2","tid":1071150,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"Propro有講 去youtube睇仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"powfessor propro？"},{"pid":"41b048c3c9076580bfe08099b2ef13c99fb08ea6","tid":1071150,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"Yau Ma Tei Station <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWaterloo Station <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868ff487fb040a53ac61d7b515152bee1a9df8c7","tid":1071150,"uid":169247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"可能跑左去旺角站上埋月台"},{"pid":"a2babcef8a4cd2dc3575a5e80397419e55a6fffb","tid":1071150,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:08:26.000Z","msg":"<code>Xboxone Contana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"31de7cdcd730ccd07f181f6b6fec2571964cf50b","tid":1071150,"uid":36673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"馮才子呢排都呃稿費味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然都好睇嘅"},{"pid":"be78ca9320bb95d95662376c3239f164e81913cb","tid":1071150,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:57:32.000Z","msg":"唔係話個女仔見到自己跳左落去咩 之後番屋企就一病不起"}]}